(277, 4, 89, 36, NULL, 'Secure Edit: software of edition and printing cards', '<TABLE id=table1 cellSpacing=2 cellPadding=1 width="100%" border=0>\r\n<TBODY>\r\n<TR>\r\n<TD width="45%">\r\n<P><STRONG>Secure Edit</STRONG> is a software allowing easy edition and printing \r\nof secure access card with bar codes, OCRB codes or PDF 417. </P>\r\n<P><STRONG>Secure Edit functions:</STRONG></P>\r\n<P><STRONG>Platforms: </STRONG>windows 95,98,2000,XP </P>\r\n<P><STRONG>Convivial use ergonomics: </STRONG>90% of manipulations are done with \r\nmouse and different kind of keyboard shortcuts. <BR></P></TD>\r\n<TD width="53%"><IMG src="" border=0></TD></TR>\r\n<TR>\r\n<TD colSpan=2>\r\n<P>The main powers of Secure Edit are as following :</P>\r\n<UL>\r\n<LI>a high use security level : \r\n<UL>\r\n<LI>Management of users by login and password \r\n<LI>Management of user access rights. \r\n<LI>Show and edition of stat of history software use by user, date and \r\nperiod.&nbsp;</LI></UL>\r\n<LI>Speedy manipulation by keyboard shortcuts. \r\n<LI>Powerful management of data bases with use of user data source and \r\npossibility of dynamic tables creation. \r\n<LI>possibility of choice between three codes (bar code, OCRB code, PDF 417 \r\ncode). \r\n<LI>Possibility of real time video capture, automatic face detection, dynamic or \r\nstatic picture treatment according the ICAO standards and direct insert into \r\ncard. \r\n<LI>Existence of development tools for treatment and modification of pictures. \r\n<LI>Simplicity of adaptation on passports, identification cards, plastic cards, \r\ndriver licenses. With a possibility of having specific states at demand. \r\n<LI>Big choice of properties for the objects inserted in the card. \r\n<LI>A very developed research function which can follows also face picture. \r\n<LI>Adaptation with all cards sizes. \r\n<LI>Saving cards on disk in order to open them another time. \r\n<LI>Possibility of serial print and in recto / back with data base link. \r\n<LI>Presence of a file informer that saves the software actions. \r\n<LI>Presence of an exhaustive help file explaining the different software \r\nfunctionalities.</LI></UL>&nbsp; \r\n<TABLE id=table1 cellSpacing=2 cellPadding=1 width="100%" border=0>\r\n<TBODY>\r\n<TR>\r\n<TD width="45%">\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P></TD>\r\n<TD width="53%"></TD></TR>\r\n<TR>\r\n<TD colSpan=2>\r\n<P>The main features of Secure Edit are the following:</P>\r\n<TABLE class=MsoNormalTable \r\nstyle="WIDTH: 746px; HEIGHT: 1310px; mso-cellspacing: 1.5pt; mso-padding-alt: 3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt 3.0pt" \r\ncellPadding=0 width=746 border=0>\r\n<TBODY>\r\n<TR style="mso-yfti-irow: 0">\r\n<TD \r\nstyle="BORDER-RIGHT: #ece9d8; PADDING-RIGHT: 3pt; BORDER-TOP: #ece9d8; PADDING-LEFT: 3pt; BACKGROUND: #cccccc; PADDING-BOTTOM: 3pt; BORDER-LEFT: #ece9d8; WIDTH: 64.96%; PADDING-TOP: 3pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: #ece9d8" \r\nnoWrap width="64%">\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center" \r\nalign=center><SPAN \r\nstyle="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-ansi-language: FR"><SPAN \r\nlang=EN-US \r\nstyle="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">Functionalities \r\n</SPAN></SPAN></P></TD>\r\n<TD \r\nstyle="BORDER-RIGHT: #ece9d8; PADDING-RIGHT: 3pt; BORDER-TOP: #ece9d8; PADDING-LEFT: 3pt; BACKGROUND: #cccccc; PADDING-BOTTOM: 3pt; BORDER-LEFT: #ece9d8; WIDTH: 8.06%; PADDING-TOP: 3pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: #ece9d8" \r\nnoWrap width="8%">\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US \r\nstyle="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><SPAN lang=EN-US \r\nstyle="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">Classic \r\nVersion</SPAN></P></SPAN></TD>\r\n<TD \r\nstyle="BORDER-RIGHT: #ece9d8; PADDING-RIGHT: 3pt; BORDER-TOP: #ece9d8; PADDING-LEFT: 3pt; BA